files <- list.files("out/disease_each/", pattern = "res.rmp.rds") %>% paste0("out/disease_each/", .)

res.r <- c()
res.q <- c()
for(i in files){
  ## read RMP
  temp.res <- read_rds(i)
  temp.res$data <- "RMP"
  res.r <- rbind(res.r, temp.res)
  
  ## read QMP
  i <- i %>% str_replace("res.rmp.rds", "res.qmp.rds")
  temp.res <- read_rds(i)
  temp.res$data <- "QMP"
  res.q <- rbind(res.q, temp.res)
}
disease.list <- res.r$disease %>% unique() 

d <- rbind(res.r, res.q) %>% filter(name != "Shannon diversity") %>% filter(name != "-1")
d$disease <- d$disease %>% str_wrap(width = 25)
d$data <- d$data %>% factor(levels = c("QMP", "RMP"))

p.list <- list()
for(i in 1:length(disease.list)){
  target <- disease.list[i]
  d.sub <- d %>% filter(disease == target)
  
  p <- ggplot(d.sub, aes(x = e, y = -log10(fdr), col = data)) +
    theme_mine() +
    geom_vline(xintercept = 0, linetype = 2, col = "gray") +
    geom_hline(yintercept = -log10(0.05), linetype = 2, col = "gray") +

    geom_point_rast(alpha = 0.5, stroke = 0) +

    theme(panel.background = element_rect(colour = "black", size = 0.5)) 
  p
  
  p.list[[i]] <- p
}
check_result <- function(target){
  target <- target %>% as.character()

  d <- rbind(res.r, res.q) %>% filter(name != "Shannon diversity") %>% filter(name != "-1")
  d <- d %>% filter(disease == target)
  d.sig <- d %>% filter(fdr < 0.05)
  
  i <- d.sig$name[1]
  shared <- 0
  rmp <- 0
  qmp <- 0  
  for(i in unique(d.sig$name)){
    temp <- d.sig %>% filter(name == i)  
    if(nrow(temp) > 1){
      shared <- (shared + 1)
    }else{
      if(grepl("RMP", temp$data)){
        rmp <- (rmp + 1)
      }else{
        qmp <- (qmp + 1)      
      }
    }
  }

  d$data <- d$data %>% factor(levels = c("RMP", "QMP"))
  p.volcano <- ggplot(d, aes(x = e, y = -log10(fdr), col = data)) +
    theme_mine() +
    ggtitle(target) +
    geom_vline(xintercept = 0, linetype = 2, col = "gray") +
    geom_hline(yintercept = -log10(0.05), linetype = 2, col = "gray") +
    scale_color_manual(values = tidy_col[c(7, 3)]) +
    geom_point(alpha = 0.5) +
    xlab("Effect size") +
    ylab("-log10(FDR)") +
    theme(legend.position = "bottom", legend.title = element_blank()) +
    geom_path(aes(group = name), size = 0.1, col = "gray50", arrow = arrow(length = unit(0.15, "cm")))
  p.volcano
  
  temp1 <- d %>% filter(data == "RMP") %>% filter(fdr < 1E-10) %>% filter(e > 0)
  temp2 <- d %>% filter(data == "RMP") %>% filter(fdr < 1E-10) %>% filter(e < 0)
  
  temp.p1 <- d %>% filter(name %in% temp1$name) %>% group_by(data) %>% summarise(e = mean(e), fdr = exp(mean(log(fdr))))
  temp.p2 <- d %>% filter(name %in% temp2$name) %>% group_by(data) %>% summarise(e = mean(e), fdr = exp(mean(log(fdr))))
  temp.p <- rbind(temp.p1, temp.p2)
  
  ## check number of significant species
  threshold <- 5E-2
  d %>% filter(data == "RMP") %>% filter(fdr < threshold) %>% dim()
  r.p <- d %>% filter(data == "RMP") %>% filter(fdr < threshold) %>% filter(e > 0) %>% nrow()
  r.n <- d %>% filter(data == "RMP") %>% filter(fdr < threshold) %>% filter(e < 0) %>% nrow()
  
  d %>% filter(data == "QMP") %>% filter(fdr < threshold) %>% dim()
  q.p <- d %>% filter(data == "QMP") %>% filter(fdr < threshold) %>% filter(e > 0) %>% nrow()
  q.n <- d %>% filter(data == "QMP") %>% filter(fdr < threshold) %>% filter(e < 0) %>% nrow()
  
  p <- (q.p / r.p)
  n <- (q.n / r.n)

  n.all <- nrow(d) / 2
  
  ## RMP (enriched)
  n.significant.r <- r.p
  n.non.r <- c(n.all - r.p)
  ## QMP (enriched)
  n.significant.q <- q.p
  n.non.q <- c(n.all - q.p)
  
  ## RMP (depleted)
  n.significant.r <- r.n
  n.non.r <- c(n.all - n.significant.r)
  ## QMP (depleted
  n.significant.q <- q.n
  n.non.q <- c(n.all - n.significant.q)

  temp <- data.frame(disease = target, p = p, n = n, case_n = d$case_n[1], cont_n = d$cont_n[1], r.p = r.p, r.n = r.n, q.p = q.p, q.n = q.n, shared = shared, rmp_only = rmp, qmp_only = qmp)
  return(temp)
}


res <- c()
for(target in disease.list){
  temp <- check_result(target)
  res <- rbind(res, temp)
}
res$disease <- res$disease %>% str_replace("\n", " ")

Combining results

stat <- read.delim("out/supple/disease_association.supple_res.tsv", header = T, row.names = 1, check.names = F)
stat <- stat %>% arrange(`Effect size`)
keep <- stat$Disease %in% res$disease
stat <- stat[keep, ]

stat$Disease <- factor(stat$Disease, levels = stat$Disease)
stat$dir <- ifelse(stat$`Effect size` < 0, "negative", "positive")
res <- stat %>% mutate(disease = stat$Disease) %>% inner_join(res, ., by = "disease")
res$disease <- factor(res$disease, levels = stat$Disease)

df <- res %>% select(disease, shared, rmp_only, qmp_only) %>% gather("key", "value", -disease)
temp <- df %>% group_by(disease) %>% summarise(n = sum(value)) %>% data.frame()
df2 <- inner_join(df, temp, by = "disease")
df2$prop <- df2$value / df2$n

## pyramid plot
df <- res %>% mutate(type = res$dir) %>% select(disease, r.p, r.n, q.p, q.n, type) %>% gather("key", "value", -disease, -type)
df$type <- df$type %>% str_replace("negative", "Negatively-associated diseases") %>% str_replace("positive", "Positively-associated diseases")
df$type <- factor(df$type, levels = c("Negatively-associated diseases", "Positively-associated diseases"))

df$data <- grepl("^r", df$key) %>% ifelse("RMP", "QMP")
df$dir <- grepl("p$", df$key) %>% ifelse("Enriched species", "Depleted species")

df$value2 <- ifelse(df$dir == "Enriched species", df$value, -df$value)
df$data <- factor(df$data, levels = c("QMP", "RMP"))


p.sig <- ggplot(df, aes(x = value2, y = disease, fill = data)) +

df <- res %>% select(disease, p, n, dir) %>% gather("key", "value", -disease, -dir)

df$key <- df$key %>% str_replace("^n", "Depleted speceis") %>% str_replace("^p", "Enriched species")

p.box <- ggplot(df, aes(x = key, y = value, col = key)) +
  theme_mine() +
  theme(panel.background = element_rect(colour = "black", size = 0.5)) +
